==制作==
影片最初是{{tsl|en|Derek Cianfrance|德里克·钱弗朗西}}未完成的计划《金属头》（''Metalhead''），讲述一位因[[耳膜|耳膜]]破裂而丧失听力的金属乐鼓手。乐队{{tsl|en|Jucifer|朱西弗}}的成员在片中本色出演。然而项目后来搁置，直到他的好友{{tsl|en|Darius Marder|达利乌斯·马德}}接受<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kohn|first=Eric|date=2021-02-02|title=‘Sound of Metal’: Darius Marder Explains His 10-Year Journey to Overnight Success|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2021/02/sound-of-metal-darius-marder-10-year-overnight-success-1234613816/|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-03-22|website=IndieWire|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223034717/https://www.indiewire.com/2021/02/sound-of-metal-darius-marder-10-year-overnight-success-1234613816/}}</ref>。2016年1月，消息指[[達珂塔·強生|達珂塔·強生]]和[[馬提亞斯·修奈爾|馬提亞斯·修奈爾]]加盟剧组，马德担任导演<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2016/01/dakota-johnson-matthias-schoenaerts-the-sound-of-metal-1201688093/|title=Dakota Johnson & Matthias Schoenaerts Team For 'The Sound Of Metal'|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2016-01-22|access-date=2019-08-07|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808010705/https://deadline.com/2016/01/dakota-johnson-matthias-schoenaerts-the-sound-of-metal-1201688093/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年7月，消息指[[里兹·阿迈德|里兹·阿迈德]]、[[奥利维亚·库克|奥利维亚·库克]]加入剧组，取代约翰逊和修奈尔，[[馬修·亞瑪希|馬修·亞瑪希]]同期加入<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/riz-ahmed-olivia-cooke-sound-of-metal-1202879738/|title=Riz Ahmed and Olivia Cooke to Star in Music Drama 'Sound of Metal'|website=Variety|first=Justin|last=Kroll|date=2018-07-20|access-date=2019-08-07|archive-date=2018-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828031957/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/riz-ahmed-olivia-cooke-sound-of-metal-1202879738/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。选角前，马德花了13年的时间物色演员，希望演员能兑现他的影片的承诺<ref name="nytimes"/>。

演员多来自失聪者群体。阿迈德为影片花了八个月的时间来准备，每天花两个小时学习[[美国手语|美国手语]]，两个小时学打鼓，两个小时上私教课，剩余时间与教练学表演<ref name="nytimes">{{cite web|last=Buchanan|first=Kyle|date=2021-01-08|title=Losing Control With Riz Ahmed|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/28/movies/riz-ahmed-sound-of-metal.html|access-date=2021-02-07|website=The New York Times|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208052833/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/28/movies/riz-ahmed-sound-of-metal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=deadline1>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/riz-ahmed-sound-of-metal-darius-marder-interview-toronto-film-festival-1202709797/|title=In The "Profound & Universal" 'Sound Of Metal' Riz Ahmed Is A Drummer Facing Hearing Loss – Toronto|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Antonia|last=Blyth|date=2019-09-05|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2019-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914194646/https://deadline.com/2019/09/riz-ahmed-sound-of-metal-darius-marder-interview-toronto-film-festival-1202709797/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马德希望阿迈德“相信他的直觉”，不让他看表演的毛片或剧本解析<ref name="nytimes"/>。

影片于2018年春季、夏季和秋季连续拍了24天<ref name="cinematography">{{Cite web |date=2020-12-08 |title=Daniël Bouquet NSC finds the delicate sound of thunder |url=https://www.cinematography.world/daniel-bouquet-nsc-finds-the-delicate-sound-of-thunder/ |access-date=2021-03-20 |website=Cinematography World |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320095819/https://www.cinematography.world/daniel-bouquet-nsc-finds-the-delicate-sound-of-thunder/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于预算有限，每个镜头马德只拍两遍<ref name=variety1>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/marders-riz-ahmed-starring-sound-of-metal-explores-deaf-identity-1203319640/|title=Marder's Riz Ahmed-Starring 'Sound of Metal' Explores Deaf Identity|website=Variety|first=Nick|last=Clement|date=2019-09-07|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2019-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909030505/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/marders-riz-ahmed-starring-sound-of-metal-explores-deaf-identity-1203319640/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。取景地包括[[大波士顿|大波士顿]]地区，主要是在{{tsl|en|Ipswich, Massachusetts|伊普斯維奇 (马萨诸塞州)|伊普斯維奇}}，其他镜头则在[[波士顿|波士顿]]、[[林恩_(马萨诸塞州)|林恩]]、[[剑桥_(马萨诸塞州)|剑桥]]、{{tsl|en|Danvers, Massachusetts|丹佛斯 (马萨诸塞州)|丹佛斯}}、[[弗雷明翰|弗雷明翰]]、[[劳伦斯_(马萨诸塞州)|劳伦斯]]、[[莫尔登_(马萨诸塞州)|莫尔登]]、{{tsl|en|Rowley, Massachusetts|罗利 (马萨诸塞州)|罗利}}、{{tsl|en|Topsfield, Massachusetts|托普斯菲尔德 (马萨诸塞州)|托普斯菲尔德}}<ref>{{Cite web |last=Slane |first=Kevin |date=2021-03-15 |title=A movie filmed in Mass. landed multiple 2021 Oscars nominations |url=https://www.boston.com/culture/entertainment/2021/03/15/sound-of-metal-oscars-nominations-massachusetts |access-date=2021-03-19 |website=Boston.com |archive-date=2021-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319144227/https://www.boston.com/culture/entertainment/2021/03/15/sound-of-metal-oscars-nominations-massachusetts |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Aucoin |first=Don |date=2020-11-11 |title=Digging deep to hear the silence, in 'Sound of Metal' |work=The Boston Globe |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/11/11/arts/digging-deep-hear-silence-sound-metal/ |access-date=2021-03-20 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210215513/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/11/11/arts/digging-deep-hear-silence-sound-metal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及比利时[[安特卫普|安特卫普]]取景<ref name="cinematography" />。

==发行==
影片于2019年9月6日在[[2019年多倫多國際影展|2019年多倫多國際影展]]{{tsl|en|Platform Prize|平台奖}}计划全球首映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/08/tiff-platform-2019-julie-delpy-riz-ahmed-1202163946/|title=Julie Delpy Made a Genetic Thriller and Riz Ahmed Is a Heavy Metal Drummer: TIFF Platform Highlights|website=IndieWire|first=Eric|last=Cohn|date=2019-08-07|access-date=2019-08-07|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808010708/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/08/tiff-platform-2019-julie-delpy-riz-ahmed-1202163946/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其后在{{tsl|en|Zurich Film Festival|苏黎世电影节}}及[[鹿特丹影展|鹿特丹影展]]放映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://iffr.com/en/2020/films/sound-of-metal|title=Sound of Metal|website=International Film Festival Rotterdam|access-date=2020-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201151920/https://iffr.com/en/2020/films/sound-of-metal|archive-date=2020-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首映礼结束的第二个礼拜，{{tsl|en|Amazon Studios|亚马逊影业}}购下影片美国发行权<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/markets-festivals/toronto-amazon-nabs-sound-of-metal-with-riz-ahmed-1203328055/|title=Toronto: Amazon Nabs 'Sound of Metal' With Riz Ahmed|website=Variety|first=Brent|last=Lang|first2=Matt|last2=Donnelly|date=2019-09-12|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913003623/https://variety.com/2019/film/markets-festivals/toronto-amazon-nabs-sound-of-metal-with-riz-ahmed-1203328055/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原计划于2020年8月14日上映<ref name=numbers>{{cite web|url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Sound-of-Metal#tab=summary|title=Sound of Metal|website=The Numbers|access-date=2020-03-02|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209035837/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Sound-of-Metal#tab=summary|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后来受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响推迟到2020年11月20日上映，12月4日登陆旗下流媒体平台[[Amazon_Prime_Video|Prime Video]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/sound-of-metal-release-date/|title=‘Sound of Metal’, Starring Riz Ahmed, Heads to Theaters in November, Amazon in December|website=SlashFilm|first=Chris|last=Evangelista|date=2020-09-09|access-date=2020-09-24|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002214115/https://www.slashfilm.com/sound-of-metal-release-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片还被[[标准收藏|标准收藏]]收录，预计于2022年发行[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]和[[DVD|DVD]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2021/03/sound-of-metal-one-night-in-miami-criterion-collection-1234621545/|title=Amazon’s ‘Sound of Metal,’ ‘Time,’ and ‘One Night in Miami’ to Join Criterion Collection|website=IndieWire|first=Zack|last=Sharf|date=2021-03-05|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305180744/https://www.indiewire.com/2021/03/sound-of-metal-one-night-in-miami-criterion-collection-1234621545/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==评价==
=== 专业评价 ===
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据230条评论，给影片打出97%的新鲜度，平均得分8.2/10。网站共识写道：“《金属之声》在里兹·阿迈德热情表演的加持，展示了失聪人群体的经历，使观众产生美好想象<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sound_of_metal|title=Sound of Metal (2020)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|publisher=Fandango Media|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209035657/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sound_of_metal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据31条评论打出82/100的平均分，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/sound-of-metal|title=Sound of Metal Reviews|website=Metacritic|publisher=Red Ventures|access-date=2021-01-08|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122153136/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/sound-of-metal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》的约翰·笛福（John DeFore）认为，影片向大家说明，接受、拥抱不可预测的变化存在必然性，没有将失聪浪漫化<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/sound-metal-1238063|title='Sound of Metal': Film Review {{!}} TIFF 2019|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=John|last=DeFore|date=2019-09-08|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2019-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190908223213/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/sound-metal-1238063|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》的大卫·菲尔（David Fear）赞赏阿迈德的表演，认为“演员的表现让影片增光不少”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-features/toronto-film-festival-2019-sound-of-metal-riz-ahmed-881361/|title=Toronto 2019: 'Sound of Metal' Gives Riz Ahmed a Perfect Showcase|website=Rolling Stone|first=David|last=Fear|date=2019-09-07|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2019-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910191557/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-features/toronto-film-festival-2019-sound-of-metal-riz-ahmed-881361/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Now (newspaper)|Now报}}》的诺曼·威尔纳（Norman Wilner）表示，具有攻击性且接近实验性质的声效让我们一直代入到鲁本的世界中，但阿迈德的表演让我们明白，他一直在躲避他的角色<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nowtoronto.com/movies/tiff2019/tiff-review-sound-of-metal-riz-ahmed/|title=TIFF review: Sound Of Metal|website=Now|first=Norman|last=Wilner|date=2019-09-11|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2019-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914040741/https://nowtoronto.com/movies/tiff2019/tiff-review-sound-of-metal-riz-ahmed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]》的埃里克·科恩（Eric Kohn）打出A−的评分，认为“阿迈德的表演非常让人信服，在演出中一直保持戏剧悬念，即便是在漫长的最后一幕的牵强氛围中，直到最终才彻底爆发出来<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/09/sound-of-metal-review-riz-ahmed-tiff-1202171828/|title='Sound of Metal' Review: Riz Ahmed Is Brilliant as a Heavy Metal Drummer Who Goes Deaf|website=IndieWire|first=Eric|last=Kohn|date=2019-09-07|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920212051/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/09/sound-of-metal-review-riz-ahmed-tiff-1202171828/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

